    "content": "I'll start by exploring the codebase to understand the existing patterns, then generate the specification.\n\n[timestamp:2026-02-12T22:06:04.323Z] 🔧 Tool: Task\nInput: {\n  \"description\": \"Find all img tags in UI\",\n  \"prompt\": \"Search the apps/ui/src directory for all `<img` tags in .tsx files. I need to find every location where images are rendered. Return the file paths, line numbers, and the surrounding code context (a few lines around each match). Be thorough - check all subdirectories.\",\n  \"subagent_type\": \"Explore\"\n}\n\n[timestamp:2026-02-12T22:06:08.663Z] 🔧 Tool: Task\nInput: {\n  \"description\": \"Explore UI component patterns\",\n  \"prompt\": \"Explore the apps/ui/src/components/ui/ directory to understand existing component patterns. I need to understand:\\n1. What existing UI components look like (structure, exports, naming conventions)\\n2. How they use className/cn utility\\n3. How they handle props spreading\\n4. Whether there's an existing pattern for loading states or skeletons\\n5. Check if there's already any lazy-image or similar component\\n6. Look at the imports pattern used (lucide-react icons, cn utility, etc.)\\n\\nAlso check apps/ui/src/components/ui/feature-image-upload.tsx and apps/ui/src/components/ui/description-image-dropzone.tsx to understand how images are currently handled in these components.\",\n  \"subagent_type\": \"Explore\"\n}\n\n[timestamp:2026-02-12T22:06:11.526Z] 🔧 Tool: Bash\nInput: {\n  \"command\": \"ls -la \\\"C:\\\\Users\\\\DylanSmart\\\\Downloads\\\\automaker-pr\\\\apps\\\\ui\\\\src\\\\components\\\\ui\\\\\\\"\"\n}\n\n[timestamp:2026-02-12T22:06:11.575Z] 🔧 Tool: Grep\nInput: {\n  \"pattern\": \"&lt;img\",\n  \"type\": \"tsx\",\n  \"path\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\DylanSmart\\\\Downloads\\\\automaker-pr\\\\apps\\\\ui\\\\src\",\n  \"output_mode\": \"content\",\n  \"-C\": 3\n}\n\n[timestamp:2026-02-12T22:06:18.875Z] 🔧 Tool: Grep\nInput: {\n  \"pattern\": \"<img\",\n  \"type\": \"tsx\",\n  \"path\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\DylanSmart\\\\Downloads\\\\automaker-pr\\\\apps\\\\ui\\\\src\",\n  \"output_mode\": \"content\",\n  \"-C\": 3\n}\n\n[timestamp:2026-02-12T22:06:23.189Z] 🔧 Tool: Bash\nInput: {\n  \"command\": \"ls -la '/c/Users/DylanSmart/Downloads/automaker-pr/apps/ui/src/components/ui/'\"\n}\n\n[timestamp:2026-02-12T22:06:25.967Z] 🔧 Tool: Bash\nInput: {\n  \"command\": \"cd \\\"C:\\\\Users\\\\DylanSmart\\\\Downloads\\\\automaker-pr\\\\apps\\\\ui\\\\src\\\" && find . -name \\\"*.tsx\\\" -type f | head -20\",\n  \"description\": \"Find tsx files in apps/ui/src\"\n}\n\n[timestamp:2026-02-12T22:06:32.167Z] 🔧 Tool: Read\nInput: {\n  \"file_path\": \"/c/Users/DylanSmart/Downloads/automaker-pr/apps/ui/src/components/ui/button.tsx\"\n}\n\n[timestamp:2026-02-12T22:06:32.355Z] 🔧 Tool: Read\nInput: {\n  \"file_path\": \"/c/Users/DylanSmart/Downloads/automaker-pr/apps/ui/src/components/ui/badge.tsx\"\n}\n\n[timestamp:2026-02-12T22:06:32.682Z] 🔧 Tool: Read\nInput: {\n  \"file_path\": \"/c/Users/DylanSmart/Downloads/automaker-pr/apps/ui/src/components/ui/card.tsx\"\n}\n\n[timestamp:2026-02-12T22:06:32.963Z] 🔧 Tool: Read\nInput: {\n  \"file_path\": \"/c/Users/DylanSmart/Downloads/automaker-pr/apps/ui/src/components/ui/loading-state.tsx\"\n}\n\n[timestamp:2026-02-12T22:06:35.547Z] 🔧 Tool: Bash\nInput: {\n  \"command\": \"cd \\\"C:\\\\Users\\\\DylanSmart\\\\Downloads\\\\automaker-pr\\\\apps\\\\ui\\\\src\\\" && grep -rn \\\"<img\\\" --include=\\\"*.tsx\\\" .\",\n  \"description\": \"Search for img tags in tsx files\"\n}\n\n[timestamp:2026-02-12T22:06:42.610Z] 🔧 Tool: Read\nInput: {\n  \"file_path\": \"/c/Users/DylanSmart/Downloads/automaker-pr/apps/ui/src/components/ui/button.tsx\"\n}\n\n[timestamp:2026-02-12T22:06:42.843Z] 🔧 Tool: Read\nInput: {\n  \"file_path\": \"/c/Users/DylanSmart/Downloads/automaker-pr/apps/ui/src/components/ui/loading-state.tsx\"\n}\n\n[timestamp:2026-02-12T22:06:43.133Z] 🔧 Tool: Read\nInput: {\n  \"file_path\": \"/c/Users/DylanSmart/Downloads/automaker-p